{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Balada Akhir Pekan: Balada Mengerikan di Akhir Pekan","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Buat bro sis yang suka komik thriller, ga usah bingung. Karena <a href=\"http://www.ciayo.com\">CIAYO Comics</a> Platform Komik Indonesia punya segudang komik dengan berbagai genre, salah satunya komik one-shot thriller. Genre ini memang tidak sepopuler genre drama atau romance di Indonesia. Tetapi komik thriller berjudul Balada Akhir Pekan ini sukses merebut perhatian pecinta komik thriller di Indonesia loh.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16599\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16599\" data-attachment-id=\"16599\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/4-129/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/4-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Eh..eh.. bu..buat apa itu gunting ?1 (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/4-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/4-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16599\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/4-4.jpg\" alt=\"Eh..eh.. bu..buat apa itu gunting ?1 (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16599\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Eh..eh.. bu..buat apa itu gunting ?1 (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sesuai dengan judulnya, komik one-shot karya Nan Nan ini memang cocok untuk menemani akhir pekan-mu. Tapi untuk pembaca yang ga kuat dengan adegan kekerasan lebih baik <em>stay away</em> ya dari komik ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16608\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16608\" data-attachment-id=\"16608\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/7-76/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/7-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ATTENTION PLEASE!\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;ATTENTION PLEASE!&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/7-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/7-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16608\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/7-3.jpg\" alt=\"ATTENTION PLEASE!\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16608\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">ATTENTION PLEASE!</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Berawal dari seorang perempuan yang bernama Yoko, pada hari Sabtu pagi. Yoko dibuat kesal karena menunggu temannya yang telat. Tak hanya itu, berbagai peristiwa buruk dengan pelayan dan pengemis pun sukses membuat akhir pekannya menjadi tambah buruk. Entah mengapa, karena kesalahan kecil orang-orang di sekitarnya saja, Yoko langsung serta merta membenci Sabtu dan membenci semuanya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16596\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16596\" data-attachment-id=\"16596\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/3-140/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/3-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Duh, Yoko kenapa sih? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Duh, Yoko kenapa sih? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/3-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/3-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16596\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/3-4.jpg\" alt=\"Duh, Yoko kenapa sih? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16596\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Duh, Yoko kenapa sih? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16605\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16605\" data-attachment-id=\"16605\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/6-98/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/6-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Darah ?! (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Darah ?! (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/6-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/6-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16605\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"Darah ?! (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Darah ?! (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pada seperempat awal komik, kamu dipastikan akan mengerenyitkan dahi. Berbagai adegan pastinya gak akan kamu duga, akan dilakukan oleh seorang Yoko. Kira-kira apa ya penyebabnya? Untuk menenangkan dirinya, Yoko pun memutuskan untuk bertemu seseorang. Namun siapa sangka ternyata Yoko malah&#8230;</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16602\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16602\" data-attachment-id=\"16602\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/5-126/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/5-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Penasaran kira-kira apa yang membuat Yoko emosi gak karuan? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Penasaran kira-kira apa yang membuat Yoko emosi gak karuan? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/5-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/5-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16602\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/5-4.jpg\" alt=\"Penasaran kira-kira apa yang membuat Yoko emosi gak karuan? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16602\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Penasaran kira-kira apa yang membuat Yoko emosi gak karuan? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Komik thriller ini memang mempunyai <em>twist</em> yang mengejutkan dan tidak disangka-sangka. Apalagi tiba-tiba pada akhir cerita Yoko menjadi ‘normal’ kembali. Komik besutan Nan Nan ini memang menawarkan thriller yang tidak biasa. Ceritanya fresh dan memiliki artwork yang sangat-sangat-sangat ‘sadis’. Yang pastinya cerita thriller ini sulit untuk ditemukan di pasaran. Setelah pembaca mengikuti alur cerita, pembaca akan dihadapkan dengan kejutan di akhir. Tak jarang, kamu juga harus berpikir sejenak untuk mencerna keseluruhan cerita saat di ending nya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16590\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16590\" data-attachment-id=\"16590\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/1-156/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/1-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Lah, kok jadi happy? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Lah, kok jadi happy? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/1-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/1-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16590\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/1-5.jpg\" alt=\"Lah, kok jadi happy? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16590\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lah, kok jadi happy? (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seluruh adegan di komik ini tanpa sensor juga loh. Jadi untuk kamu penggemar komik thriller, kamu akan tercengang dengan apa yang ditawarkan <em>author</em> pada cerita ini. Penasaran gimana ceritanya? Kira-kira apa saja yang dilakukan Yoko sampai membuat kolom komentar komik one shot thriller ini bergidik seram?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_16593\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16593\" data-attachment-id=\"16593\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/balada-akhir-pekan-balada-mengerikan-di-akhir-pekan/attachment/2-114/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/2-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/2-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/2-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16593\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/2-4.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-16593\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Penasaran kira-kira apa yang diperbuat Yoko? Kira-kira apa penyebab Yoko berbuat seperti itu? Untuk lihat langsung cerita thriller yang bener-bener thriller, bro sis bisa langsung baca komiknya dengan klik tautan di bawah ini.</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/balada-akhir-pekan/detail\"><strong>BALADA AKHIR PEKAN</strong></a></h1>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"94fcbca4-2afc-5e1d-9c45-a96c9276571e"}}}